WEBVTT

00:02:59.200 --> 00:03:01.896
because if you're texting
a text line, you want help.

00:03:01.920 --> 00:03:03.096
So she gets the address

00:03:03.120 --> 00:03:05.296
and the counselor triggers
an active rescue

00:03:05.320 --> 00:03:07.320
while they're texting back and forth.

00:03:08.000 --> 00:03:11.216
And then it goes quiet --

00:03:11.240 --> 00:03:15.880
23 minutes with no response
from this girl.

00:03:17.160 --> 00:03:19.616
And the next message that comes in says --

00:03:19.640 --> 00:03:21.256
it's the mom --

00:03:21.280 --> 00:03:24.856
"I had no idea, and I was in the house,

00:03:24.880 --> 00:03:27.360
we're in an ambulance
on our way to the hospital."

00:03:28.200 --> 00:03:30.080
As a mom that one just --